title: DC/OS 1.9.0
description: DC/OS 1.9 includes many new capabilities for Operators, and expands the collection of Data and Developer Services with a focus on:
features: Tools for Production Operations - Monitoring and troubleshooting for distributed apps.
Broader Workload Support - From traditional apps to machine learning.
